Here is a good .gitignore for your Python / Streamlit dashboard project.
This will prevent uploading unnecessary files to GitHub.

Create a file named:

.gitignore
and paste this inside:

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.sqlite3

# Virtual environment
venv/
env/
ENV/
.venv/

# Streamlit
.streamlit/

# VS Code
.vscode/

# Mac
.DS_Store

# Windows
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Build files
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/

# Secrets / config
.env
.env.local

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.bak

# Zip / downloads
*.zip
